ons, is aprotected rightunder theUS Constitution.\", \"from\": 10296, \"to\": 10431, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Filming and observing ICE agents\", \"from\": 10296, \"to\": 10328}, {\"ngram\": \"their operations\", \"from\": 10369, \"to\": 10385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ICEtoldAl Jazeerathat \\\"obviously, ICE does not conduct immigration enforcement operations in foreign countries,\\\" but Sala suggested that it was not entirely obvious that officers with the agency would not perpetrate violence at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 10433, \"to\": 10674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10550, \"end\": 10554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emiliano_Sala\", \"score\": 0.999993986341798, \"rank\": 6.013694264367465e-06, \"text\": \"Sala\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emiliano_Sala\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emiliano_Sala\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ICE\", \"from\": 10467, \"to\": 10470}, {\"ngram\": \"immigration enforcement operations\", \"from\": 10488, \"to\": 10522}, {\"ngram\": \"foreign countries\", \"from\": 10526, \"to\": 10543}, {\"ngram\": \"officers\", \"from\": 10603, \"to\": 10611}, {\"ngram\": \"the agency\", \"from\": 10617, \"to\": 10627}, {\"ngram\": \"violence\", \"from\": 10649, \"to\": 10657}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 10661, \"to\": 10673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Officers with ICE, he toldRTL 102.5radio, \\\"do not guarantee they are aligned with our democratic security management methods.\\\"\", \"from\": 10676, \"to\": 10802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ICE\", \"from\": 10690, \"to\": 10693}, {\"ngram\": \"our democratic security management methods\", \"from\": 10758, \"to\": 10800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is a militia that kills,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 10804, \"to\": 10845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a militia\", \"from\": 10813, \"to\": 10822}]}, {\"sen