erations\", \"from\": 11144, \"to\": 11167}, {\"ngram\": \"the agency\", \"from\": 11206, \"to\": 11216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If mitigating risks is the goal, said Alessandro Zan, a member of European Party representing Italy'sDemocratic Party, \\\"it's paradoxical to entrust it to those who are the first to commit crimes, operating with violence, and killing innocents in cold blood.\\\"\", \"from\": 11219, \"to\": 11477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11257, \"end\": 11271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alessandro_Zan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alessandro Zan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alessandro_Zan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alessandro_Zan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"risks\", \"from\": 11233, \"to\": 11238}, {\"ngram\": \"the goal\", \"from\": 11242, \"to\": 11250}, {\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 11273, \"to\": 11281}, {\"ngram\": \"European Party\", \"from\": 11285, \"to\": 11299}, {\"ngram\": \"Italy'sDemocratic Party\", \"from\": 11313, \"to\": 11336}, {\"ngram\": \"crimes\", \"from\": 11407, \"to\": 11413}, {\"ngram\": \"violence\", \"from\": 11430, \"to\": 11438}, {\"ngram\": \"innocents\", \"from\": 11452, \"to\": 11461}, {\"ngram\": \"cold blood\", \"from\": 11465, \"to\": 11475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In Italy, we do not want those who tramplehuman rightsand act outside any democratic control,\\\" said Zan.\", \"from\": 11479, \"to\": 11584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11483, \"end\": 11488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9999925199360948, \"rank\": 7.4800651936427015e-06, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rightsand act\", \"from\": 11528, \"to\": 11541}, {\"ngram\": \"any democratic control\", \"from\": 11550, \"to\": 11572}, {\"ngram\"